{"tid":1107934,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有啲痴L線屋企人？","createTime":"2019-04-15T14:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T15:31:54.000Z","uid":171117,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9dd87e824ad1f68c2fd65b143a40428f9a7b4e80","tid":1107934,"uid":171117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T14:56:21.000Z","msg":"「乜都唔洗做冇付出，死廢柴」<br />\n我唔洗返工唔洗交家用既？<br />\n<br />\n「唔係係屋企就係出去」<br />\n咁仲可以去邊？鐵閘同木門中間條隙？<br />\n<br />\n「當我奴隸呀要我煮飯洗碗？」<br />\n全職主婦除左呢啲你仲有咩要做？瞓？<br />\n<br />\n「交果少少錢唔好以為自己好巴閉，自私到死」<br />\n幾千銀家用已經係我最大支出都自私，成份糧比哂你啦不如<br />\n<br />\n「病你唔好返黎傳染人，你死你事我唔想知」<br />\n病我去睇醫生啦睇你有春用咩<br />\n<br />\n唔同你嘈唔代表覺得你啱，係唔想家嘈屋閉同慳返啖氣喳仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"014be7fd5af3ed9f32b1a97583dda79c503e6486","tid":1107934,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:00:08.000Z","msg":"點解樓主唔屌7返佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375d2b6b18e5c996ebab18d6493daebe53cf1316","tid":1107934,"uid":131664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:08:11.000Z","msg":"唔係係屋企就係出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5490ffc6ed3477d12e4e3a848c26c0f1f2869fb6","tid":1107934,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:09:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0138c42966ab7958019ff881e85146ac03d39d3e","tid":1107934,"uid":755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:10:46.000Z","msg":"同我老母一樣"},{"pid":"da0e77bb3cabb5d40ceaf89385ed59ce01fe76c3","tid":1107934,"uid":55770,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:13:23.000Z","msg":"鐵閘同木門中間條隙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑咗出聲"},{"pid":"d2767dbf490c2eb197fc76eee12970b173fbdb71","tid":110793